                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Gullwing Coast. The wind will steal your footing if you let it. My flock and I watch the cliff so the trainers bound for Gaviota do not feed the tide."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Neptune holds the Water gym in the port below. Deep team, deeper patience. Do not rush the sea."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Gaviota Port is past the spray. Watch your step on the cliff and mind Neptune when you reach the water."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I watched Neptune ride a Wailord through the harbor mouth at dawn once. Nobody believes a gull-keeper. The gulls believe me. The gulls were there."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Gull-Keeper Hano",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
        },
